## Game Play

The theme is taken from the movie *The Good, the Bad and the Ugly*. A knowledge of the movie isn't required for the game play.


The player is hinted as to the theme of the random word. And that word is represented by a series of underscores.

The user's input is captured by a keyboard where they can select a letter. With the sixth incorrect guess, Tuco hangs and the game play ends.
